# Soma SQL Conventions

- All tables have user_id UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES auth.users(id)
- All tables have created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW()
- Primary keys are UUID with gen_random_uuid()
- Deduplication via UNIQUE(user_id, source_id) on event tables
- Every table gets a corresponding RLS policy after creation
- Use event_date DATE (not TIMESTAMPTZ) for daily health data
- Canonical biometric metric names: hrv_rmssd, resting_hr, sleep_hours,
  sleep_deep_hrs, sleep_rem_hrs, body_weight_lbs, body_fat_pct, vo2_max, steps
- Index pattern: (user_id, date_column DESC) for all time-series tables